I"	<ol>
  <li>Stop MySQL service:
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>systemctl stop mysql
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Edit <code class="highlighter-rouge">/etc/mysql/my.cf</code>:
    <div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>innodb_force_recovery=4
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Fix permissions (optional):
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">chown</span> <span class="nt">-R</span> mysql:mysql /var/lib/mysql
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Start MySQL service:
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>systemctl start mysql
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Export all existing databases:
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>mysqldump <span class="nt">-A</span> <span class="o">&gt;</span> all_databases.sql
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Stop MySQL service:
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>systemctl stop mysql
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Remove <code class="highlighter-rouge">ib*</code> files:
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">rm</span> /var/lib/mysql/ib<span class="k">*</span>
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Remove/comment this line from <code class="highlighter-rouge">/etc/mysql/my.cf</code>:
    <div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>#innodb_force_recovery=4
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Start MySQL service:
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>systemctl start mysql
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Re-import previously exported databases:
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>mysql &lt; all_databases.sql
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
</ol>

